which causes injury to both of them. Kuze&nbsp;
offers to merge his ghost with her, saying&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:26.720 --> 00:13:30.800
that he will always be there for her no matter&nbsp;
what. She refuses, because according to her,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:30.800 --> 00:13:35.200
this is where she belongs, and this place is her&nbsp;
true nature. Moments after, Cutter's men from the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:35.200 --> 00:13:40.400
overhead aircraft aim a shot at Kuze, instantly&nbsp;
killing him. Mira shouts in agony and sadness.&nbsp;&nbsp;

