00:13:49.680 --> 00:13:53.760
and recovers Mira, who is still alive. He is in&nbsp;
awe after seeing her still surviving despite the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:53.760 --> 00:13:58.720
attacks. He asks Mira what her true name is, and&nbsp;
she responds by saying "Motoko". Batou helps her&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:58.720 --> 00:14:02.880
get up and recovers her strength. Aramaki then&nbsp;
confronts Cutter after having spoken to the Prime&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:02.880 --> 00:14:06.800
Minister about tagging him as a criminal. Cutter&nbsp;
is charged with multiple crimes he committed&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:06.800 --> 00:14:11.280
against the state including Dr Ouelet’s death.&nbsp;
Aramaki contacts Mira through mind communication&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:11.280 --> 00:14:16.000
and gets her consent to execute Cutter. He shoots&nbsp;
Cutter three times as he falls into his own pool.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:16.000 --> 00:14:19.920
Mira sees her own grave for the first time. Her&nbsp;
mother accompanies her, and they are happily&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:19.920 --> 00:14:24.960
reunited. She tells her mother that she does&nbsp;
not need to come to the cemetery anymore. Life&nbsp;

00:14:24.960 --> 00:14:29.680
continues in the futuristic city. Aramaki still&nbsp;
gives the orders, the team assembles again,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:29.680 --> 00:14:32.880
Operations with section 9 continue,&nbsp;
and Mira is ready for her next mission.

